        "* **Time-Varying Indirect Effect ($\\beta_t \\cdot \\alpha_{2,t}$):** In contrast, the indirect path shows a stable, materializing **harmful effect** mediated through $M$. As the study progresses, the mediator offsets the treatment's benefits, introducing a source of risk that grows in certainty (narrowing HDI).\n",
